{
  "stem": "5639.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they, they--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, look.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to understand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's very difficult to understand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For a normal mind, living under normal human circumstances, one is richer, one is poorer, one is fatter, one is thinner, but they're all normal circumstances.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To understand the mentality of a group that was told they are doomed to die, and couldn't believe that we have to die.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'd done nothing wrong, socially.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are not criminals rejected by the society.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no distinction because-- between poor and rich, orthodox and secular, educated and ignorant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All Jews have to die because Jew is not allowed to live.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you just can't see yourself in the group of people who are going to die.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you hope.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For what you hope, that the war will finish before they will have time to implement it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew that the ultimate is total destruction.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that time, we were not sure what form the total destruction will take, or is taking.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were rumors we were-- which were unacceptable to our human mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have a point of reference.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Our grandparents, and our parents remember German, remember that in certain areas, they were acting violently, brutally, but they were civilized people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, the concept that they can murder people was impossible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We believed that we might be starved to a point that we will die from starvation, that the starvation can be such that it can incubate a disease, an epidemic, from which you can die.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That we will be deprived of medication, of saving ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But to take people, to murder them, was inconceivable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Inconceivable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very comfortable position.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1938, he suggested to my mother that we move to Israel, to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to them, you can go.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
